show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/7KHPbe
show.description: Ananya, a spirited college girl longing for the affection absent from her emotionally distant father, finds herself irresistibly drawn to Vikram — her father’s best friend and her childhood crush. Twice her age, emotionally reserved yet quietly magnetic, Vikram is asked to look after Ananya as her behavior raises concern. What begins as care soon ignites a forbidden connection, stirring old feelings in Ananya and awakening something Vikram has long buried. Torn between guilt and desire, Vikram resists, afraid to hurt the one person who makes him feel alive again.
